  "style_summary_en": "Showa-era legacy ambiance in Ginza 8-chome.\n'Arai Style' — rooted in orthodox Edomae with the chef's personal interpretation.\nTuna signature — sourced directly from Toyosu Market + Yamayuki tuna + four distinct cuts per serving.",
  "style_summary_jp": "銀座8丁目の昭和時代老舗の雰囲気。\n「アライスタイル」— 正統派江戸前をベースにシェフ独自のアプローチ。\nマグロのシグネチャー — 豊洲市場直接仕入れ + ヤマユキのマグロ + 4種類の異なる部位を提供。",
  "holistic_signature_en": "Multilayered expression of tuna.\n\nTokyo authenticity meets chef-driven character.",
  "holistic_signature_jp": "マグロの多層的な表現。\n\n東京の正統性とシェフの個性が共存。"
